<er>Inspect</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety> <def>Inspection.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Thomson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inspection</ent>⟦br⟧
